snippet.title: HELI 100 - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
HELI 100 coming June 13th 2019 to App Store and Google Play!

HELI 100 is Tree Men Games take on bullet hell / shmup games. Try to survive 100 missions of enemies in a small arena type of battle, be fast, dodge bullets, use power-ups and defeat the enemies. Who will be the best player of HELI 100? Leaderboards start at mission 100!

App Store:
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/heli-100/id1460229292

Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.treemengames.heli&hl=en
